data.description: Move in ready with quality furniture, kayaks, and lawncare equipment included in the sale of this home! Listen to the gentle sounds of the stream from your deck and bedroom windows! Enjoy the peaceful views of the wooded green-belt backyard! Recent improvements to this home include the installation of a whole house generator which brings comfort if there is ever a loss of electricity; staying cool in with summer with the ductless split-units AC/ heating back-up; cozy warm in the fall & winter months with a propane ''wood stove'' in the living room. The chimney has been cleaned and new liner installed as well as freshly painted rooms. You can enjoy the quiet mountain living experience while, at the same time, accessing the top-rated amenities of Wallenpaupack Lake Estates. This home has 1 bedroom with bunk beds on the main floor with 2 additional bedrooms, loft area and full bathroom with a skylight on the upper floor. The dining area is large enough to seat 10 at the gorgeous wood table (included). The family room with access to the backyard is on the lower level. There are two decks; one in the front of the home and another accessed from the dining room area. The BBQ grill is hooked up to the main house propane, so you won't run out of propane while grilling your favorites with family and friends! The one car sized garage is accessed from the back of the home. As part of the WLE community, you have privileges to access 2 private lakes, beaches, 2 outdoor pools, an indoor pool & gym, lodges & game room as well as access to the private community marina on the big lake, Lake Wallenpaupack!
